      <h1 class="title">
      Manuel Castells no Le Monde diplomatic
  </h1>
  <span class="publishing-info">
  <span class="date">
    11 de Março de 2007, 0:00
  </span>
  <span class="author">
    , por Software Livre Brasil
  </span>
  <span class="comments">
     - <a href="/branco/blog/manuel-castells-no-le-monde-diplomatic#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>sem comentários ainda</span></a>
